data.description: 3% Seller contribution to Buyer costs with acceptable offer! Single story 3 bed 2 bath home with 3 car garage on over 8000sf lot in Double Diamond. This well maintained property offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living area provides plenty of room for relaxation and entertainment. Move-in ready With brand new paint & carpet. Tankless on-demand hot water & energy efficient solar panels for lower power bills. Lovely yard and covered patio, perfect for outdoor activities or gardening. Located in a tranquil neighborhood, this home offers a peaceful retreat while still being close to schools, parks, and amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home! Solar will be owned by Buyer, typically generating $100/month NVEnergy credit.
